      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWBOURNE FOCUS (1) has a strong record this trip with 13 wins and five placings from 19 starts. Recorded a 4 length win (19.50) in a NG last time at this track. Expected to be in the finish. LITTLE BIT SUPER (2) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 0.8 lengths from the winner Gus And Glory in second(19.17) at Bulli. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Expected to feature. TRAVELLING GEM (7) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Was too tough when scoring last time over 318m at Dubbo in a NG (18.10). Has a good record here at this journey including seven wins. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Likely to be in the finish. AUSSIE BLEND (8) has a solid strike rate at this track and distance.",
